OL,5,G2035 40 Originals at the BBC: Volume 2
OL,6,     FAnother celebration of the
OL,7,     Foriginal outings of 40 classic
OL,8,     Fsongs that were so good, it was
OL,9,     Finevitable that they'd end up
OL,10,     Fbeing covered by others.
OL,11,G2300 40 Originals at the BBC
OL,12,     FA compilation of songs that became
OL,13,     Fbigger hits for the artists who
OL,14,     Fcovered them. These are the
OL,15,     Fincredible original versions, with
OL,16,     Fartists including Gladys Knight
OL,17,     Fand Dolly Parton.
OL,18,G0120 Nostalgia
OL,19,     FA man's return to his hometown of
OL,20,     FNaples stirs up a past he has kept
OL,21,     Fburied. Contains some strong
OL,22,     Flanguage. [2022]
